# Annotation Property: schema1:legislationApplies (legislationApplies)

AnnotationAssertion(schema1:category schema1:legislationApplies "issue-1156")
AnnotationAssertion(schema1:domainIncludes schema1:legislationApplies schema1:Legislation)
AnnotationAssertion(schema1:isPartOf schema1:legislationApplies <http://pending.schema.org>)
