AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment schema1:ownershipFundingInfo "For an <a class=\"localLink\" href=\"http://schema.org/Organization\">Organization</a> (often but not necessarily a <a class=\"localLink\" href=\"http://schema.org/NewsMediaOrganization\">NewsMediaOrganization</a>), a description of organizational ownership structure; funding and grants. In a news/media setting, this is with particular reference to editorial independence.   Note that the <a class=\"localLink\" href=\"http://schema.org/funder\">funder</a> is also available and can be used to make basic funder information machine-readable.")
