# Annotation Property: schema1:publishingPrinciples (publishingPrinciples)

AnnotationAssertion(schema1:domainIncludes schema1:publishingPrinciples schema1:CreativeWork)
AnnotationAssertion(schema1:domainIncludes schema1:publishingPrinciples schema1:Organization)
