# Annotation Property: schema1:ratingValue (ratingValue)

AnnotationAssertion(schema1:domainIncludes schema1:ratingValue schema1:Rating)
AnnotationAssertion(schema1:rangeIncludes schema1:ratingValue schema1:Number)
AnnotationAssertion(schema1:rangeIncludes schema1:ratingValue schema1:Text)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment schema1:ratingValue "The rating for the content.<br/><br/>

Usage guidelines:<br/><br/>

<ul>
<li>Use values from 0123456789 (Unicode 'DIGIT ZERO' (U+0030) to 'DIGIT NINE' (U+0039)) rather than superficially similiar Unicode symbols.</li>
<li>Use '.' (Unicode 'FULL STOP' (U+002E)) rather than ',' to indicate a decimal point. Avoid using these symbols as a readability separator.</li>
</ul>
")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label schema1:ratingValue "ratingValue")

