AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment schema1:unnamedSourcesPolicy "For an <a class=\"localLink\" href=\"http://schema.org/Organization\">Organization</a> (typically a <a class=\"localLink\" href=\"http://schema.org/NewsMediaOrganization\">NewsMediaOrganization</a>), a statement about policy on use of unnamed sources and the decision process required.")
