AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment schema1:CDCPMDRecord "A CDCPMDRecord is a data structure representing a record in a CDC tabular data format
      used for hospital data reporting. See <a href=\"/docs/cdc-covid.html\">documentation</a> for details, and the linked CDC materials for authoritative
      definitions used as the source here.")
