AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label schema1:CableOrSatelliteService "CableOrSatelliteService")
SubClassOf(schema1:CableOrSatelliteService schema1:Service)

# Class: schema1:CafeOrCoffeeShop (CafeOrCoffeeShop)

