AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment schema1:Class "A class, also often called a 'Type'; equivalent to rdfs:Class.")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label schema1:Class "Class")
EquivalentClasses(schema1:Class rdfs:Class)
SubClassOf(schema1:Class schema1:Intangible)

