AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment schema1:DisagreeAction "The act of expressing a difference of opinion with the object. An agent disagrees to/about an object (a proposition, topic or theme) with participants.")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label schema1:DisagreeAction "DisagreeAction")
SubClassOf(schema1:DisagreeAction schema1:ReactAction)

