AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment schema1:DislikeAction "The act of expressing a negative sentiment about the object. An agent dislikes an object (a proposition, topic or theme) with participants.")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label schema1:DislikeAction "DislikeAction")
SubClassOf(schema1:DislikeAction schema1:ReactAction)

