AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment schema1:EmployerReview "An <a class=\"localLink\" href=\"http://schema.org/EmployerReview\">EmployerReview</a> is a review of an <a class=\"localLink\" href=\"http://schema.org/Organization\">Organization</a> regarding its role as an employer, written by a current or former employee of that organization.")
