# Class: schema1:MonetaryAmount (MonetaryAmount)

AnnotationAssertion(schema1:source schema1:MonetaryAmount <http://www.w3.org/wiki/WebSchemas/SchemaDotOrgSources#FIBO>)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment schema1:MonetaryAmount "A monetary value or range. This type can be used to describe an amount of money such as $50 USD, or a range as in describing a bank account being suitable for a balance between £1,000 and £1,000,000 GBP, or the value of a salary, etc. It is recommended to use <a class=\"localLink\" href=\"http://schema.org/PriceSpecification\">PriceSpecification</a> Types to describe the price of an Offer, Invoice, etc.")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label schema1:MonetaryAmount "MonetaryAmount")
SubClassOf(schema1:MonetaryAmount schema1:StructuredValue)

