AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment schema1:NewsArticle "A NewsArticle is an article whose content reports news, or provides background context and supporting materials for understanding the news.<br/><br/>

A more detailed overview of <a href=\"/docs/news.html\">schema.org News markup</a> is also available.")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label schema1:NewsArticle "NewsArticle")
