AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment schema1:PostalCodeRangeSpecification "Indicates a range of postalcodes, usually defined as the set of valid codes between <a class=\"localLink\" href=\"http://schema.org/postalCodeBegin\">postalCodeBegin</a> and <a class=\"localLink\" href=\"http://schema.org/postalCodeEnd\">postalCodeEnd</a>, inclusively.")
