AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment schema1:UserReview "A review created by an end-user (e.g. consumer, purchaser, attendee etc.), in contrast with <a class=\"localLink\" href=\"http://schema.org/CriticReview\">CriticReview</a>.")
