AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment schema1:legislationLegalValue "The legal value of this legislation file. The same legislation can be written in multiple files with different legal values. Typically a digitally signed PDF have a \"stronger\" legal value than the HTML file of the same act.")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label schema1:legislationLegalValue "legislationLegalValue")
